---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/sections/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/sections/Footer.astro';
import Button from '../../components/ui/button/Button.astro';
---

<html lang="en" data-theme="dark" class="dark">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title="Rast Biznisa — Case Study"
      description="Case study for an Instagram experiment focused on business-oriented content, audience engagement and organic growth testing."
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <Button href="/portfolio" variant="outline" size="sm">← Back to Projects</Button>
      </div>

      <section class="card-surface p-8 md:p-10">
        <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[var(--accent)] mb-3">Case Study</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-foreground m-0">Rast Biznisa — Instagram Experiment</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[color:var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          An experimental Instagram project created to test content hooks, messaging structure and growth-oriented content ideas for a business-focused audience.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-sm">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/3 p-4">
            <p class="text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] m-0">Project Type</p>
            <p class="font-semibold mt-2 m-0 text-foreground">Growth Experiment</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/3 p-4">
            <p class="text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] m-0">Role</p>
            <p class="font-semibold mt-2 m-0 text-foreground">Content Strategy & Testing</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/3 p-4">
            <p class="text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] m-0">Tools</p>
            <p class="font-semibold mt-2 m-0 text-foreground">Instagram, ChatGPT, Canva</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/8 bg-white/3 p-4">
            <p class="text-[color:var(--color-text-muted)] m-0">Year</p>
            <p class="font-semibold mt-2 m-0 text-foreground">2026</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-8 border-[color:var(--border)]" />

        <div class="space-y-8 text-[color:var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Overview</h2>
            <p>
              Rast Biznisa was created as a practical experiment to understand how business-focused Instagram content performs when different hooks,
              formats and messaging styles are tested intentionally.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Problem</h2>
            <p>
              Organic growth becomes difficult when content is inconsistent, generic or poorly positioned.
              Business-oriented pages especially need clear hooks and strong formatting to earn attention.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Goal</h2>
            <p>
              The goal was to test practical content approaches and identify which ones are more effective at generating attention,
              engagement and clearer content positioning.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Approach</h2>
            <p>
              I used the page as an experimental environment for testing different post structures, educational angles,
              stronger hooks and content presentation styles. The purpose was not only to post consistently,
              but to observe what makes business content more engaging and more understandable.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Outcome</h2>
            <p>
              The project generated practical insights about content clarity, hook design and how audience attention can be influenced
              by stronger framing and positioning.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">What This Project Shows</h2>
            <p>
              This case study reflects a growth-oriented mindset: using content as an experiment,
              learning from response patterns, and improving through iteration instead of guessing.
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <Button href="https://www.instagram.com/rastbiznisa_bg?igsh=bHVvczFncHYwbjNk&utm_source=qr" variant="primary" size="sm">View Instagram</Button>
          <Button href="/portfolio" variant="secondary" size="sm">Back to Projects</Button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
